#### Save Release Notes
Create a file named `RELEASE_NOTES_v[VERSION].md` in the `releases/` folder for reference.

### 6. Safe Production Deployment

#### ‚ö†Ô∏è CRITICAL: Vercel Production Deployment Safety
Before deploying to production, ensure you're following safe deployment practices:

```bash
# ‚úÖ SAFE - Production deployment workflow
# 1. Ensure you're on main branch with merged changes
git checkout main
git pull origin main

# 2. Verify everything is ready for production
npm run build  # Test build locally
npm run test   # Run all tests

# 3. Deploy to production explicitly
